title: Swedish Pro-Migrant Protest Violates Coronavirus Crowd Ban
description: A demonstration outside a Swedish Migration Board facility in the city of Gothenburg this week violated government restrictions on gatherings of crowds meant to halt the spread of the Wuhan coronavirus.
